  ],
  "remarks": "Ibrahim Achmatov is the General Director of JSC Kizlyar Electromechanical Plant, a Russian military industry company. The plant specialises in the development and manufacture of aircraft ground control and diagnostic systems, and the production of attachments and on-board equipment. The company produces DZ-UM lock for SU-25 fighters, which are used by Russian military forces to attack Ukraine. JSC Kizlyar Electromechanical Plant fulfils Russia’s state defence orders.",
